comment: Mack (UTA) cleanly strips the ball from Bledsoe (PHO).
Gobert (UTA) makes contact to Bledsoe (PHO) with his arms on the screen and does not give him room to avoid the contact.
Ingles (UTA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Booker (PHO) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Chriss (PHO) makes incidental contact with Hayward (UTA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Chandler (PHO) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Hayward (UTA) that does not affect his shot attempt.
[Incidental or immaterial] RATR and LATR show Chandler (PHO) extends his leg out and sets the screen on Hayward (UTA) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Lyles (UTA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Bledsoe (PHO) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Ingles (UTA) and Booker (PHO) make incidental contact with one another as they try to secure the loose ball.
Hayward (UTA) makes contact with Booker (PHO) that affects his ability to secure the loose ball.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
RATR shows Chandler (PHO) is inside the restricted area when he makes contact with his arms to Hayward's (UTA) body and affects his driving shot attempt.
[Detectable with stop watch] Booker (PHO) does not inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
Ingles (UTA) legally contests Booker's (PHO) jump shot attempt.
Booker (PHO) commits a take foul on Hayward (UTA).
